    "notes": "This was pressed at Presswell, identified by (PR) P in runout.  Most likely a 1977-1978 pressing.\nSKBO 3403 printed on spine and os's.  SKBO-3403 printed on labels.\nGatefold sleeve.  Originally included custom printed lyric inner sleeves.\nRed Labels with pink Capitol are designated:\nRecord 1, Side 1\nRecord 1, Side 2\nRecord 2, Side 1\nRecord 2, Side 2\n\nRunouts are etched except for \"MASTERED BY CAPITOL\" which is stamped.\n\n℗ 1973 EMI Records Limited\n© 1973 Apple Records, Inc.\nPrinted in U.S.A.\nAll selections previously released.\nDouble album originally released in 1973.",
